---
title: Balsamic Bacon-Wrapped Chicken with Roasted Potatoes and Wedge Salad
description: Tonight, enjoy a luxe chicken meal from your own dining room! Tender chicken is wrapped in smoky bacon and drizzled with a sweet and tangy balsamic glaze. Served alongside are umami-packed Parmesan roasted potatoes and a fresh wedge salad.
